<br>
Your gods ...all of them...are nothing but egos personified, and your attempts to worship and appease these so-called dieties will lead only to their continued inflated self-importance and infinite arrogance.<br>
<br>
It is your own powers and your own self worth that will serve you in this life, and the contrived pursuit to gain the approval of some big-headed creature will only cause you distraction and veer you from the true path of self-improvement. <br>
<br>
These tales you cling to were written by church leaders who are more interested in gaining wealth and power for themselves and keeping the populace in check than doing humanity a good turn. <br>
<br>
Halus<br>
